title: Tyrant Esports Club Main Team LF Master/Challenger jungler.
body:
Due to our jungler going on a break for holidays, TEC is looking to replace our old challenger jungler. 
If you think you got what it takes in OOL and wanna make it to OCS with us, either add TEC Miazma 
Or the Tyrants Esports Clubs Coach glacial for more details.
